    org.eclipse.stardust.engine.api.model.Activity.getDefaultPerformerID()
    Superseded by Activity.getDefaultPerformer(). The old behavior was to silently resolve conditional performers if possible and return the ID of the resolved participant. Migration to the new API probably requires testing for ConditionalPerformer and a call to ConditionalPerformer.getResolvedPerformer() instead.
